README
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Name: Presentation Timer
Description: A presenation timer that can be used to show the presenter how 
	     much time has elapsed. It can also warn them when their alloted 
	     time is running out be changing the background color.
Version: 0.1
Author: Wiktor Starzyk

USAGE
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

spacebar	starts and stops the time
r 		resets the timer
q 		quits the application

Currently the timer is hardcoded for 2 minutes.
